# New Computer Science Course: Game

## Target Audience
This course would be for 11th or 12th graders who have taken a computer science class before

## Where does it fit
This could either be run as a saturday elective course or a one semester elective. Students would recieve 1 math elective credit. 
Student must have taken either python, AP CSP or AP CSA. 


## General description
This course will teach students the fundamental elements of basic game design. By the end
of this course, students wil have a better understanding of the process of game design, have more knowledge
about game design related careers, and be able to create their own game. 
